Dividindo a base treino/teste

set.seed(32)

dispneia_initial_split <- initial_split(dispneia, prop = 0.8,
                                        strata = "dispneia")

dispneia_train <- training(dispneia_initial_split)

dispneia_test <- testing(dispneia_initial_split)
